      "id": "1b64750c-f3ba-803d-ba8b-de02ccc4d6e6",
      "type": "numbered_list_item",
      "text": "Recommenders are often evaluated in Backtests based on metrics such as accuracy and not on whether the recommendation actually improved the learner’s learning performance.",
