    {
      "id": "1b64750c-f3ba-80a2-9cf8-dd0b1e4d339b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors introduce RCL4ER, which makes recommendations by mixing self-supervised learning and reinformecement learning in the model’s output layer. Authors also explore a trained KT model while testing 3 distinct data augmentation techniques. Testing on 4 distinct public datasets shows promisisng results.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b64750c-f3ba-80a2-9cf8-dd0b1e4d339b",
        "parent": {
